.PP
    GNU Awk                 >= 5.1.0
.PP
    gpg                     >= 2.2.40
.PP
    grep                    >= 3.6
.PP
    sed                     >= 4.9
.PP
    wget                    >= 1.21
.PP
    whereis                 >= 2.36.1
.PP
.B The optional dependencies are as follows:
